Class EnemyImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.EnemyImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    models.Character, models.Enemy, models.Entity
    public class EnemyImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements models.Enemy
    EnemyImpl is a class that implements Enemy and its contracts. It generates Enemy entities, each initialized with a position, set amount of health and an Ai.
